Join the kinkiest BDSM dating community

We have tested Fetlife for you and this sheet aims to enlighten you on its reliability.

Fetlife: Reviews, Ratings and Rating!

Fetlife fetlifeapp.com was one of the few BDSM sites to surprise us positively by its quality. Fetlife is a historical site in the BDSM online dating. Indeed, Fetlife was one of the instigators of the BDSM sites but continues to exist and to be one of the leaders in the field.

Profiles on Fetlife

Possible encounters: BDSM meeting, fetish dating, swinger dating, libertine dating

This site has founded over time a BDSM community and fetishists almost unmatched in France. Fetlife has a great diversity in its user profiles. The profiles are very well stocked and you can often find personal videos on the profiles.
The quality of the members

The quality of the members of Fetlife is simply very good. Varied, active, open, mature, parity … are praise that come back regularly to describe the user base of this site. The proportion of women and couples registered is very reasonable and offers a wide choice of partners to meet. The members are very open-minded and are not reluctant to discover new sexual practices. Although they often use the webcam on the site, they are looking for real relationships above all else.

The effectiveness

Fetlife is an effective site for meeting men, women and couples from the BDSM and fetish community. This site has filled us enough in our test by giving us the opportunity to interact and meet lots of women. The BDSM chat on Fetlife is very active and there is really something for everyone (submissive, dominant, bondage, fetishist …). Not as effective as C-Dating, certainly, but this BDSM and fetish dating site is far from being ridiculous and does not have to bend your head! It is also the second most effective BDSM site for online dating!

Conclusion on Fetlife

Fetlife is a very good BDSM and fetishist dating site! Our conclusions on the test of the Fetlife site are very favorable and allow us to offer it without any fear. The site has many assets: a quality interface, a large BDSM community and fetishists present, a chat very active … If you have the desire to meet new people for BDSM or fetishist relationships, Fetlife is a good choice.
